{"tid":727804,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（記錄）唔食零食一個月","createTime":"2018-07-03T09:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T04:20:56.000Z","uid":96080,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d6572c2c657b0b5ba2ecd0415df4ccaade61e080","tid":727804,"uid":96080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"真係好鬼死鍾意食垃圾<br />\n正餐食嘅分量好正常(8小時內完成)<br />\n但衰在食零食 搞到減唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由7.1開始到依家 正餐冇食少到 反而多咗<br />\n但神奇地輕咗1.1lb 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n為咗健康 唔會再嘥錢買零食<br />\n希望我講得出做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b42bae97129834c241ea10cd3029f02a3826c80","tid":727804,"uid":60508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"一個月洗幾錢買零食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aeb626c9181dad5b640a7ec764e3e53380d1de","tid":727804,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"51925b4bcfcbea330b725dcd75d8fc681bfda2f0","tid":727804,"uid":96080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5aeb626c9181dad5b640a7ec764e3e53380d1de","tid":727804,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T19:28:50.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0433af2ceaddff2dd058a996359c19f6e24bea6","tid":727804,"uid":123969,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T19:31:29.000Z","msg":"但零食真係好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/033056_7042a2490ec41a6d8ff321887cae1686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.